                    <span>This book is extremely usefull for anyone who wants to establish a new business, or promote an existing one. Detailed, step by step instructions, help you leverage your skills and personality, focus  on the right product/service, apply the right marketing strategy and win all the business you can afford.
<br />
<br />Nothing left to luck, examines every possible aspect of your business. Extremely usefull for self-employed or small business individuals.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">What an Incredible Book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>11</span>
